comments: Maledon (OKC) makes contact to Wright's (SAC) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Hield (SAC) legally contests Bazley's (OKC) driving shot attempt and any contact that occurs is incidental.
Hield (SAC) reaches backwards for the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Brown (OKC) during his putback shot attempt.
Dort (OKC) runs by Hield (SAC) and marginal contact occurs as he briefly places an arm against him.
Hield (SAC) makes contact to Bazley's (OKC) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) extends an arm towards Dort (OKC) and marginal contact occurs as he goes around the screen.
Holmes (SAC) extends his leg into Dort's (OKC) path and delivers contact that affects his ability to defend the play.
Wright (SAC) moves towards Bazley (OKC) and marginal body contact occurs before he makes clean contact with the ball.
Dort (OKC) commits a take foul on Holmes (SAC).
Roby (OKC) commits a take foul on Holmes (SAC).
